00:48:08,360 --> 00:48:11,080
You got to get that protein in there.

558
00:48:12,640 --> 00:48:16,680
I was just wondering,
if you wanted to go see a movie with me.

559
00:48:21,080 --> 00:48:24,200
Yeah, sure.
Yeah, I do.

560
00:48:25,360 --> 00:48:27,280
Cool, um, let me see...

561
00:48:27,320 --> 00:48:31,920
