Victoria feels it's only fair
to kill Edwards mate...

717
01:01:32,800 --> 01:01:34,400
...given he killed hers.

718
01:01:34,560 --> 01:01:36,480
An eye for an eye.

719
01:01:37,040 --> 01:01:40,080
Threaten him.
- Edward would know who did it!

720
01:01:40,320 --> 01:01:42,000
And he'd come after you.

721
01:01:42,640 --> 01:01:44,880
I don't think he will.

722
01:01:45,840 --> 01:01:48,560
After all, how much could
you mean to him...

723
01:01:49,280 --> 01:01:52,400
...if he left you here unprotected?

724
01:01:53,920 --> 01:01:57,040
Victoria won't be happy
about me killing you.

725
01:01:57,280 --> 01:01:59,520
But I can't help myself.

726
01:01:59,680 --> 01:02:02,560
You're so mouth-watering.
- Please, don't!

727
01:02:02,960 --> 01:02:06,080
I mean, you'd helped us.
- Shhhh!

728
01:02:06,400 --> 01:02:09,680
Don't be afraid.
I'm doing you a kindness.

729
01:02:09,840 --> 01:02:15,520
Victoria plans on killing you
slowly, painfully,

730
01:02:16,000 --> 01:02:20,320
...whereas I'll make it quick.
I promise.

731
01:02:21,120 --> 01:02:23,280
You will feel nothing.

732
01:02:28,720 --> 01:02:30,640
Edward, I love you.

733
01:02:32,720 --> 01:02:35,200
I don't believe it.

734
01:03:42,440 --> 01:03:44,200
Dad, I saw them!

735
01:03:44,280 --> 01:03:47,160
What's the matter?
