736
01:03:47,280 --> 01:03:48,120
What you mean in the woods?

737
01:03:48,160 --> 01:03:50,080
Bella, what the hell were you doing
out in the woods?

738
01:03:50,160 --> 01:03:53,800
They are wolves.
I mean, they're like huge wolves!

739
01:03:53,880 --> 01:03:57,080
Are you sure about that, Bella?
- Yeah, I just saw them.

740
01:03:57,240 --> 01:03:59,720
They were after... something.

741
01:04:00,040 --> 01:04:03,600
Wolves? You saw?

742
01:04:06,600 --> 01:04:09,520
Alright.
Well, Harry,

743
01:04:10,400 --> 01:04:11,520
...feel like going hunting?

744
01:04:11,640 --> 01:04:13,320
Can you get some of
your guys together?

745
01:04:14,120 --> 01:04:16,840
Sure, yeah. I'll...
I'll just...

746
01:04:18,120 --> 01:04:20,440
<I>I know that those wolves
will be dead.

747
01:04:21,400 --> 01:04:23,720
<I>And Laurent would have told her
I'm unprotected.

748
01:04:24,760 --> 01:04:26,360
<I>Victoria.

749
01:04:27,560 --> 01:04:29,240
I should go to the station.

750
01:04:29,400 --> 01:04:31,560
Dad, you should...
You should go.

751
01:04:32,040 --> 01:04:34,360
You can just stay in the house?

752
