01:06:32,760 --> 01:06:38,040
Bella, do you remember,
when walked on the beach in La Push?

767
01:06:39,000 --> 01:06:41,480
The stop...

768
01:06:44,360 --> 01:06:49,240
The story...
The story about the cold ones.

769
01:06:51,640 --> 01:06:55,080
I guess, I understand why that's
the only part you remember.

770
01:07:02,360 --> 01:07:06,360
There must got to be something
You can do...

771
01:07:06,440 --> 01:07:08,760
No.
I'm in it for life.

772
01:07:09,960 --> 01:07:12,040
May be we should just
get out of here for a while.

773
01:07:12,600 --> 01:07:15,960
We'll just leave.
Just you and me.

